def generate_operation_id_for_path(*, name: str, path: str, method: str) -> str:
    operation_id = name + path
    operation_id = re.sub("[^0-9a-zA-Z_]", "_", operation_id)
    operation_id = operation_id + "_" + method.lower()
    return operation_id
